    p
      | Dream Verse is meant for individuals aged 13 and above. If you&apos;re under 13, please seek permission from your parents or your imaginary friend.
    h5.mt-2 2.2 Account Creation
    p
      | To join the fun, you can register directly with your email or unleash your inner superhero by using your Google account. We promise not to reveal your secret identity.
  .user_generated_content.mt-3
