    p
      | As much as we appreciate imagination, we won&apos;t tolerate any bullies raining on the parade. If you encounter any mean-spirited individuals, report them faster than a superhero in a cape.
    h5.mt-2 3.3 Privacy Policy
    p
      | Your secret identity is safe with us! We only ask for your email, name, and birthdate to ensure you&apos;re old enough to dream big. We won&apos;t share your information unless compelled by an army of supervillains.
  .platform_usage.mt-3
    h2 Platform Usage
    h5.mt-2 4.1 Post Formats
    p
      | Unleash your creativity with short story-like tweets (500 characters or less) or create grand adventures with our fancy wysiwyg editor. The choice is yours!
    h5.mt-2 4.2 Content Possibilities
    p
      | You can post text, GIFs, images, or combine them to create a masterpiece. Just don&apos;t forget to include some unicorn magic!
  .moderation.mt-3
